{"title":"纺轮（外一首）","authors":["赵士旺"],"dates":[{"year":1983,"month":10,"day":27}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"纺轮（外一首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赵士旺"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不能老钻在树底下躲雨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不能老躲在洞穴里避风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不能老靠几片树叶遮掩粗糙的皮肉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不能老披几张兽皮御寒过冬。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您在杭州湾建立了人的王国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"探求人的衣食住行，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"匠心设计人的衣著，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"思维牵动了纺轮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从此，丢掉了身上披挂的树叶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巧手织出“河姆”牌的珍品。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今，我凝视手上的草帽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身穿的涤纶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"床上的凉席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"藤椅的回纹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想起皇帝的金缕玉衣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宫女的襦衫长裙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仿佛都看见您设计的花纹……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}